rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc2e5793ea61e1d7ec0d48246c8251ed15333ea","tid":2205563,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n數學唔夠好真係死穴嚟"},{"pid":"e4467d81e3cb67c020ce7ef154f114a08b25330c","tid":2205563,"uid":366321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"推薦用khan academy<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 深入淺出,而且每課都有練習清concept<br />\n加油啊"},{"pid":"9536cf2e4578e3325ec3714afb9dfcbd94c57ffe","tid":2205563,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"文科仔唔識數點識欣類物理既美<br />\n俾本書你睇都唔知個公式點derive <br />\n由thomas calculus 讀起 <br />\nmartrix<br />\node<br />\npde<br />\nmultivariable of calculus<br />\nvector calculus<br />\ncomplex number<br />\nnumerical ....<br />\n再上網搵啲 introduction to classical mechanics 之類讀"},{"pid":"80d37a77c12371366d7e25f3623d6e7363b251cc","tid":2205563,"uid":56260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"已經講到數學唔算好<br />\n搞清楚你想學既係科普定hardcore物理先"},{"pid":"56c066fabd3d9c94157350db41fbabc24696673c","tid":2205563,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"Young &amp; Freedman: University Physics with Modern Physics<br />\nStephenson: Mathematical Methods for Science Students <br />\nThorton &amp; Marion: Classical Dynamics of Particles and Systems<br />\nGriffiths &amp; Schroeter: Introduction to Quantum Mechanics <br />\nGriffiths: Introduction to Electrodynamics <br />\nBlundell: Concepts in Thermal Physics"},{"pid":"3f82c59113d247bb6baa3f4fe143f2f61e869e7b","tid":2205563,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"一開始去圖書館搵d字典咁厚既physics書黎睇下先<br />\n都係intro to 乜乜 or fundamental of 乜乜個d<br />\n讀好中學calculus再去睇calculus based既大學yr1 physics<br />\n跟#10個list去睇"},{"pid":"5d6a8f970ac9c1f5bcdb6aec6e4945c7f1aa8429","tid":2205563,"uid":236413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"買中學教科書"},{"pid":"bde4a10cf0fb6cacdb6078d1ad4882516d4da8a5","tid":2205563,"uid":55620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"中學書先囉<br />\n不過我冇記錯既話<br />\n中學書已經cut到比小學生睇<br />\n難既全部比佢cut鳩哂咁濟<br />\n你有冇大學讀phy果啲 問佢地拎下啲note睇囉...<br />\n不過數學差好難明... <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">[black]利申 8大乞食phy 成日諗係咪入錯 好撚難[/black]</span>"},{"pid":"56a889cc2d9f9bb1ded2cbc80a98d5e582c4e3e4","tid":2205563,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T19:21:18.000Z","msg":"搵陳堅"},{"pid":"40f3a287e37ed96fefc9af5fbb535673a5c6208d","tid":2205563,"uid":198539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"睇完天能？"},{"pid":"e87ac64754d105e3f255f48c3caab32ce012c32c","tid":2205563,"uid":370374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"算啦唔識 linear algebra 同 multivariable calculus 冇資格做物理人 (利申冇資格)<br />\n你可能係想了解下物理背後嘅思考過程而非其本科知識，如果係gum Thomas Kuhn 嘅 The Structure of Scientific Revolutions 應該有用。Carl Sagan 大部份嘅書都得。"}]}